  "title": "Junior Marketing Associate",
  "description": "<p>If you’re aiming for a career that offers growth, development, and practical skills, this Sales Consultant role gives you a strong head start. We welcome individuals with no background in sales — your learning journey begins with us.</p>\n<h3><strong>Your Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Engaging customers in person through events and business campaigns</li>\n  <li>Understanding client needs and recommending suitable solutions</li>\n  <li>Sharing product knowledge in a clear and confident manner</li>\n  <li>Contributing to a team culture built on performance and support</li>\n  <li>Participating in structured training to sharpen your communication and leadership abilities</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What You’ll Gain From This Role</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Weekly payout + strong commission structure</li>\n  <li>Attractive incentives tied to your performance</li>\n  <li>Regular upskilling workshops</li>\n  <li>Opportunities to progress into senior or leadership roles</li>\n  <li>Travel experiences for exposure and learning</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You’ll walk away with solid confidence, valuable communication skills, and a strong foundation in sales — all while being part of a team that pushes you to be your best.</p>\n<p>If you see yourself growing in a fast-moving environment, reach out and apply today.</p>",
